# AI Chatbot

## What I Built
A minimal AI chatbot with a Node.js Express backend and a vanilla JavaScript frontend. The chatbot maintains conversation context and is deployed with a live frontend and backend.

## API and Model
API: OpenRouter  
Model: openai/gpt-4o-mini  

Why backend only: API keys placed in frontend JavaScript can be extracted by anyone using browser DevTools or network inspection, allowing unauthorized usage and billing abuse. Using a backend ensures the key remains secure and never exposed to the client.

Fallback provider: Google Gemini API. Switching requires changing:
1. Base URL to https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/openai/
2. Model name to gemini-1.5-flash

## Live Deployment
Frontend: https://ai-chatbot18.netlify.app/ 
Backend: https://aichatbot-98pp.onrender.com

